    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you won't find one in better shape\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and it drives like a total dream. It\u2019s super clean inside and out, and I'm really looking for it to go to a good home where it'll be loved just as much. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
