    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving double-VANOS variable valve timing system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This specimen is mechanically flawless: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, rod bearings have been addressed, and the VANOS system is fully overhauled. The chassis retains its factory rigidity with refreshed bushings and an impeccable underside. Documented with a comprehensive service file, this is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
